at the farmers of the South lose\nannually $27,000,000 by marketing\ntheir cottonseed. His -estimate i3\ngained through the following facts:\nAn average crop of 12,000,000 bales\nwill afford a yield of 6,000,000 tons,\nof cottonseed. The cottonseed mills\nof the South report annually that of\nthis amount only 3,500,000 tons are\ncrushed at their refineries.\nAllowing a bushel to an acre for\nnlantinc. the farmer keeps at home\n500,000 tons of cottonseed, orenougni\nto plant 30,000,000 acres m the snowy\nstaple.\nThis will leave a clear 2,000,000\ntons of cottonseed which are either\nthrown away, left to lie on the ground\nand rot. as in olden days, or the seed\nare placed in the ground as the fer\ntilizer. It is estimated that out of this\namount of seed wasted there is $2,\n000,000 worth of lint, which is used\nfor all sorts of practical 'purposes\nabroad, and $25,000,000 worth of\ncottonseed oil which is never extract\ned and refined, which, Dr. McCand\nless states, is of no earthly value as\na fertilizer.\nThis experiment, with this state\nment of the waste that is going on\naround the country, will doubtless\ncause more cottonseed to be placed\non the market.\nThe blooming rose is beautiful\nBut the blushing bride more dutiful,\nAll the crimson tints vou like to see are\nher's\nBy taking Rocky Mountain Tea.\nE. T. Whitehead Co.\n\"Father, what are wrinkles?\"\n\"Fretwork, my son,' fretwork,\"\nreplied pater familias, confidently.\nPhiladelphia Inquirer.\nObstinate cases of constipation and\nnasty, mean headaches prom ply dis\nappear\" when vou take De Witt's Little\nEarly Riser Pills. Sold by E. T. White\nhead Co.\nCivilization is certainly advancing\nwheji the college boys get to passing\nresolutions against hazing.\nTo cure a cold first move the bowels.\nBees Laxative Cough Syrup acts gently\non the bowels, drives out the cold,\nclears the head. It's pleasant to take\nand mothers highly recommend it for\ncolds, croup and whooping cough.\nGuaranteed to give satisfaction or mon\ney refunded. Equally good for young\nand old. Sold bv E. T. Whitehead\nCo.\nCan Cancer Be Cured?\nIt Can.\nWe want every man and woman in\nthe United States to know what we\nare doing We are curing Cancers,\nTumors and Chronic Sores without\nthe use of the knife or by X-ray, and\nare endorsed by the Senate and Leg\nislature of Virginia.\nWE GUARANTEE OUR CURES.\nKELLAM HOSPITAL,\nNo. 1615 West Main Street,\nRichmond, Virginia.\n5-J3-'o7-iy\nExecutrix Notice.\nHaving qualified as executrix of\nof the last will and testament of the\nlate W. A. Staten, this is to notify\nall persons having claims against said\nestate to' file same with me or my\nattorney, Albion Dunn, Esq., on or\nDeiore tne zbtn day ot September,\n1908. or thisjioticfi will 1 iorirJ\nin bar of their recovery. All per\nsons inaeDcea to said estate will\nplease make immediate settlement\nThis September 23d, 1907.\nOlivia Staten,\n9-26-6t Executrix W. A. Staten\n30 DAYS' TREATMENT FOR $1.00\nSatisfaction guaranteed\not monej .refunded.\nFOR ALL KIDNEY BLADDER\nTROUBLE, RHEUMATISM\nAND LUMBAGO\nI f- A dose at bed. time usi\na- ally relieves, the most\nsevere case before morning.\nPINEULE \"MEDICINE CO\nCHICAGO. U. S. A;\nSold by E. T. Whitehead Co\nLaxative\nCough Syrup\nCONTAINS HONEY AND TAR\nchest and bronchkl tubes? ,thrat'\n\"A feMitt to the taste\nMaple Sugar\"\nChildren Like It\nPINEULES\nBACK-ACHE\nFor sale by E. T. Whitehead Co.\ni33aRZS5BZaESa\nWe\nTrust\nDoctors\nIf vou are suffering from\nimpure blood, tmn Diooa, uc\nbility, nervousness, exhaus\ntion, you should begin at once\nwith Ayer's Sarssparilla, the\nSarsaparilla you have Known\nall your life. Your doctor\nknows it, too. Ask him about it.\ntti.. twi. 1. dallr action of the bowel,\npoisonm,. products are ab.orbed. causinK n-\nall vegetable.\nKado by O. Ayer Co.. towcll. Kas.\nPAIR VIGOR.\nyers\nAGUE CURE. -CHERRY\nPECTORAL.\nWe fcave bo aoereto Ve pnblisH\nthe formulae of all our medioinea.\nonuments\nam able\nYou\nneed